## pmon

A process monitor for linux

```
$ pmon 23245

rss       vms       pss       swap      uss       cpu (%)   mem (%)
1.06G     2.52G     1.05G     0B        1.05G     0.00      6.83
1.06G     2.52G     1.05G     0B        1.05G     0.00      6.83
1.12G     2.58G     1.11G     0B        1.11G     64.20     7.22
1.12G     2.58G     1.11G     0B        1.11G     0.00      7.22
```

### Install

```
pipx install pmon
```

